Developer Terms of Use
des: Given your birth date, the Chinese Zodiac skill tells you your Chinese zodiac animal. There are overall twelve Chinese zodiac animals. Depending on the year you were born, you zodiac animal could be one of the following: Rat, Ox, Tiger, Rabbit, Dragon, Snake, Horse, Goat, Monkey, Rooster, Dog, or Pig.
